1815,PullRequestEvent,2018-08-01 02:09:01+00:00,88241992,rsalmei/clearly,6652853,rsalmei,,,205289556,MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjA1Mjg5NTU2,"Independent client and server, connected by gRPC",open,False,27,"Finally we'll be able to let a server running all the time, collecting celery events, independent of any connected clients! This will allow to use `Clearly` as a flower substitute.

The software architecture is quite different now. We have a threaded `EventListener`, that captures celery events only, collecting tasks and workers in an LRU memory, and converting to an immutable format before passing up to the next phase, via a Queue.
Then there's the `StreamingDispatcher`, another threaded processor, that maintains and synchronizes events with interested parties or observers. For each new event, it tests whether a connected client would like to see it, and if yes, generates the missing gaps in states and sends them to another Queue, one specific to that particular client.
And finally there's the `ClearlyServerServicer`, a gRPC server in a `ThreadPoolExecutor`, that accepts connections, and redirects to the streaming dispatcher if a realtime capture was requested, or to the listener memory for currently persisted results.

The code is way better, way more testable, and almost all modules has 100% code coverage.",https://api.github.com/repos/rsalmei/clearly/issues/27,,,2018-08-01T02:09:01Z,25,1738,89,34,OWNER,[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/rsalmei/clearly/pull/27.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/rsalmei/clearly/pulls/27/commits,010,"['f5ddea6218e0b3e4a97fa77bb2495c343023e494', '378951d940aad914ae68d6ce089d5535ebd8a636', '47ac2d662eb197f55299c91ccb8880751da95f4f', '0d8d11b00f107f99c8f2e33741e1c1bb63b5b303', '01c7e418d70ed1b0c28d5b34658eb9237d4d9211', '03fd725a5058fd68fbcfb2a9b1ebed58527b000b', 'fefe5d4844bb4f98435d094c444e979a0730c6ce', '5de7911d93c58fc661a8a39d47361eff8e3a12ee', 'c86d101e565d8f960ced269b62819bb9cc1b4a62', '0e2439db9a41641d699e8fe0c279e521a9fb0353', '3220f8e2f9f13c4c3f46a7f168aa00095cc359ed', '8e566f018de5197dd6802482f05e53c0a9871ce0', '2eadfd90e4319b1e4587dbd73f5064f1781c23b4', 'a5fbfd5cf3092488f48716ace4162b0b0d42f3c1', '42d704c37a934bef5f1c34e84555a7ec6280f373', 'bec83b6bd0f779afa1f5d17862e439425c482b4d', '73bbb131370c4df281d1e8ae953aae02d05458ff', '27838dc114f195e9e7eec1fe059e0288e6724708', '5c7f79f155d36d7009a20012862be2d9900f5396', 'f6d3cfd5d78b5bf2f2ceddefc1216b784c59644d', 'e51cdbbc5182500bd33bbd074e95bf65edeeeb90', 'd1f5f715fe2339e010f02870c63b3767cfea8aee', 'e5563482882825175435a35d53f1abeed811e15e', '1b12b1961f7f34071cfda317f6935f6623d77bb7', '2b2a8366bcd77e90f59e3a9f559ad7ac2eef031b', '37349760b72044a96a253bec2d86e8bdf6cfe782', 'efd326299f87d16e1f3f9d0ccfd2ea14dfefdd51', 'ac4835f76494331ef562ff9dece32676159a6e0e', '8c75a438e2a1f5fa0e686c2f78687ed0e94aee2f', 'e676f5aa4797c9d2d276899d7ebd025cce3c37cf', '7bd527c9fb022b8a6acc501327950d5aa659c61b', 'e5893fc8b1ee0243e50f379718fb575e978f7ce5', 'aedaac0047c1b1cd7ca1582b0e69b9efb6d90c74', '11f535a2547480d481f86821077c11feea9db510', 'e9c112e11135888eb0b470f8faa42b076b909aae', '125fdcde0b518c8fdfc973e49bd6fb4be2c0b99a', '3175a64af6bf57bf82f8c475f7cbb96153dab486', '3682e55b552f780f48518545aa05a30f8cc5697d', '5aca0