2168,PullRequestEvent,2015-08-02 19:54:57+00:00,8313091,miso-belica/sumy,4634933,JulianGriggs,,,41423445,,Adding SumBasic Summarizer,open,False,30,I used sumy for an academic paper a few months back and figured it would nice to contribute some of the additions I made.  This pull request adds the SumBasic algorithm for summarizing.  SumBasic is a frequency based approach that attempts to limit redundant information by decreasing the weighting given to words found in previously included sentences.  SumBasic is often used as a baseline summarization system that new methods are compared to.  More information can be found at: http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~nenkova/papers/ipm.pdf.,https://api.github.com/repos/miso-belica/sumy/issues/30,,,2015-08-02T19:54:56Z,8,263,3,5,[],[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/miso-belica/sumy/pull/30.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/miso-belica/sumy/pulls/30/commits,010,"['03532aab92b681855bd13c839dac3193a255d880', 'f84aa5f651417b01ee7b7f5f217e0f7e6a30fdb4', '115a9a11f5f40d09c3205f4bd900fb21a6a4c36b', '93d2743de417e315d3d0164ebf058227accd10af', 'eef2354b2dc61c4b0f0e0893d61a715faaae1d4c', '6d83a2fa569e3b4efdd6bea63135fc690b52800c', 'd851da66639e50b812ba3f364b87788e8346eeab', '33c5505011145a203b655eb68b8688a3c4a015a8', '744bf96954e31d80ddd21549805d5d0fc8fae3e7', '41762d1d6324683d26cb9417eb89578f3c4290d4']"
