7916,PullRequestEvent,2018-03-02 07:28:10+00:00,744916,gem/oq-engine,2463856,micheles,316546.0,gem,170381610,,Splitting all the sources upfront,closed,False,3463,"Splitting the MultiPointSources upfront improved the task distribution. Splitting the AreaSources upfront improved it even more. Here I am splitting all splittable source typologies upfront and the task distribution is a bit better. The cost is a longer startup time of the tasks, but it is minor. All in all, the improvement is not at all spectacular, but it is a simplification of the current approach, 40 lines of code were removed. 
Since the distribution is so good, I am increasing the default size of the tiles from 20,000 to 30,000 sites, to produce a bit less tasks.",https://api.github.com/repos/gem/oq-engine/issues/3463,,2018-03-02T07:28:09Z,2018-03-02T07:28:10Z,31,176,209,15,CONTRIBUTOR,[],"[{'login': 'ptormene', 'id': 350930, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/350930?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/ptormene', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ptormene/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",[],,,,,['enhancement'],https://github.com/gem/oq-engine/pull/3463.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/gem/oq-engine/pulls/3463/commits,010,"['f88b05b8a7d77e1f53bf7c6fef9696172adecde3', '6a2e732bf09d82d8e7b4d7bc1bfe1b0e3ada92aa', '3226b8303d15097abbc957088407c3a00645cf3c', '337bcca5842b24c770f83966a800e719e6c8791a', '595de84de14514a67877ba590b0e02f4d0d626ee', '5521e1b55d6870615d7c69d36c2461508b223579', 'ca6e04f173a4124aa6ee71038ea88bebaaf5c647', '71dffab95fc381ea19364fcdd85ea0ef3d79edd2', 'fc3c22a99411842174f3cdd406e8d12c27b99f1f', 'f840084e052588d579fef6f8c8256535b6740675', '08cbc66c6ffd3dee7bb02a5b443cb35eebdc3de7', 'd7cc05090a621f7cffe1a51e06f6342617ed17f0', '63384a489f8bbdf8e9e7de362e10d26f22d1eaca', '9bcdd71590ec1351a334e730a1c55aa9f46e20fd', '343dd4d55640b6a97fdceb6e277d71e2727cbc7f', '723bbe84d0c03b585540a7f