9199,PullRequestEvent,2018-06-14 04:48:04+00:00,89379547,zostera/django-bootstrap4,82315,dyve,1092877.0,zostera,175951896,MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MTc1OTUxODk2,fix rendering of checkbox,closed,False,75,"Hi, 

Currently checkboxes are still rendered in the Bootstrap 3 way: the checkbox input is rendered within the checkbox label. Because of changes in the way checkboxes are handled in Bootstrap 4, checkboxes rendered like this, don't work in Bootstrap 4 compatible themes. 

This pull request changes the rendering to the Bootstrap 4 way.",https://api.github.com/repos/zostera/django-bootstrap4/issues/75,2018-06-14T04:48:03Z,2018-06-14T04:48:03Z,2018-06-14T04:48:03Z,2,23,11,1,NONE,[],[],[],dyve,82315.0,User,False,[],https://github.com/zostera/django-bootstrap4/pull/75.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/zostera/django-bootstrap4/pulls/75/commits,010,"['2acdddf299995b8a003e1884da62ac413a24d7a9', 'ee57f528ac057ee08594319f08619a13782402fa']"
