9223,PullRequestEvent,2015-04-28 07:34:05+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,1529400,crepererum,1157480.0,inveniosoftware,34240460,,docker: image slim-down,open,False,3060,"* Slims down docker image by building on top of less bloated base image
  and only install what is really required. Also purges unneeded
  packages, flushes caches and clean temporary files. All these parts
  should not be in a production image and are also not required by
  developers. You can still install components when extending the
  Invenio base image.

* Removes dpkg package docs from the production image because admins
  should not use a slim docker image as a knowledge base.

* Sets correct MySQL username and db variable in boot script since we
  rely on them and Invenio might change these defaults.

Signed-off-by: Marco Neumann <marco@crepererum.net>",https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3060,,,2015-04-28T07:34:05Z,1,27,2,2,[],[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/3060.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/pulls/3060/commits,010,['de47f7bf976ce89e651adcef50ac24534f3af592']
9230,PullRequestEvent,2015-03-31 10:22:20+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,189798,jirikuncar,1157480.0,inveniosoftware,32308785,,access: removal of external authentications,open,False,2974,"* INCOMPATIBILITY Removes proprietary authentication protocol for
  robotlogin.  (closes #2972)

* INCOMPATIBILITY Removes external authentication engines. Please use
  `invenio.modules.oauthclient` or Flask-SSO instead.  (closes #1083)

Signed-off-by: Jiri Kuncar <jiri.kuncar@cern.ch>",https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/2974,,,2015-03-31T10:22:20Z,1,32,5287,25,[],[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/2974.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/pulls/2974/commits,010,['716f882c6e64a4506445bc74f6d54cb078feb8a3']
9233,PullRequestEvent,2016-05-09 08:26:56+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,11770726,ddaze,1157480.0,inveniosoftware,69310568,,BibFormat: optional record recommender,open,False,3616,"* NEW Record recommender loads and displays recommendations on
  each record page. The recommendations are calculated with the speared
  python package the invenio-record-recommender.

* Loads the calculated recommendations from Redis.

* Creates /record/*id*/recommendations endpoint.

* Introduces CFG_RECOMMENDER_REDIS and CFG_RECOMMENDER_PREFIX config
  used to set the Redis instance from where the recommendations should
  be loaded.

* Renders recommended records in JavaScript after the record is loaded.

* Logs clicks on recommended records to webstat.

