9518,PullRequestEvent,2018-02-28 17:59:16+00:00,14829536,pydata/numexpr,5999769,robbmcleod,1284191.0,pydata,171989571,,Fixes test bench in Python 3,closed,False,297,"The test bench did not run on Python 3 because of the usage of long,
