10437,PullRequestEvent,2018-08-30 15:17:27+00:00,15510254,openfisca/openfisca-core,216452,Morendil,1794404.0,openfisca,212116747,MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjEyMTE2NzQ3,Experimental computation of dependencies based on AST parsing,open,False,719,"#### New features

- The `/variable/:name` endpoint in Web API now provides a list of variables depended on
  - This is on a per-formula basis and the field is named `dependencies`

#### Status

Experimental; feedback sought on the feature and its possible extensions (see below). For now, consider this PR a prompt for a discussion of whether this approach would be valuable, to whom and under what conditions.

#### Possible improvements
- [ ] Replace the code in legislation explorer that regexes formula source code to link to dependants
- [ ] Support reverse dependency computation
- [ ] Handle the tough case - dependencies via extracted (non-formula) methods
- [ ] Provide a CLI interface to output e.g. Graphviz to dump the entire graph
- [ ] Provide some error handling ?
",https://api.github.com/repos/openfisca/openfisca-core/issues/719,,,2018-08-30T15:17:27Z,1,25,1,4,NONE,[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/openfisca/openfisca-core/pull/719.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/openfisca/openfisca-core/pulls/719/commits,010,"['91aa42b2bf21e7ff39ed0c490391beca3ee99c8a', '149b481a44c8cad2e01add6c5c813a0f2347cc8d', '5030e03921eafeaf619b41b4cbcd28fdd827c246', 'f4480f5c0fd9ae0f5e0ee7470fb4e0955b79200a', 'a42c2a51c199213766e82a894c7943e91b8b9b2b', '1761a0aa4d2abdd10500178adecf57cd825e3024']"
10440,PullRequestEvent,2018-01-19 20:13:52+00:00,15510254,openfisca/openfisca-core,11834997,fpagnoux,1794404.0,openfisca,157589614,,Handle memory overflows,closed,False,601,"Depends on #598.

_Attention: this PR is opened towards `update-taxipp-v20` to make the diff clearer. Once #598 is merged, the target branch must be changed to master_

#### New features

- Improve [`holder.get_memory_usage`]((http://openfisca.readthedocs.io/en/latest/holder.html#openfisca_core.holders.Holder.get_memory_usage)):
  - Add `nb_requests` and `nb_requests_by_array` fields in the memory usage stats for traced simulations.

- Enable intermediate data storage on disk to avoid memory overflow
  - Introduce `memory_config` option in `Simulation` constructor
    - This allows fine tuning of memory management in OpenFisca

For instance:

```
from openfisca_core.memory_config import MemoryConfig
config = MemoryConfig(
    max_memory_occupation = 0.95,  # When 95% of the virtual memory is full, switch to disk storage
    priority_variables = ['salary', 'age']  # Always store these variables in memory
    variables_to_drop = ['age_elder_for_family_benefit']  # Do not store the value of these variables
    )
```",https://api.github.com/repos/openfisca/openfisca-core/issues/601,2018-01-19T20:13:51Z,2018-01-19T20:13:51Z,2018-01-19T20:13:51Z,19,522,158,14,OWNER,[],"[{'login': 'sandcha', 'id': 6567910, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/6567910?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/sandcha', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/sandcha/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",[],fpagnoux,11834997.0,User,False,[],https://github.com/openfisca/openfisca-core/pull/601.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/openfisca/openfisca-core/pulls/601/commits,010,"['b038e9ac0941d11b7e1b964cf466f731d271a17c', '499c92a7c278eeaeecc31260b249c6034c6bcbb9', 'b5d0c9a517517d230b8d33a0645a7a6db743b571', '06abe4eb54ce9d38c95d0c9a5b739958ddb543ca', '5f0dc41fd5699fe1fbf55f22e4845c0e6bb1405c', 'd9d83b4b4e2f18960da5b30979d8c0acf8e788d8', 'e91de644de16b18cf13a0f423828298c7f06b6c0', '58de5fb1e0e915ede213d367fd953055722dedd0', '1549f9fc607053b52447e53b253acddc890419de', 'cdafb21295d87961f0874184f2a236a00fe7a2db', '11a62f258c0f632b9135399c6ad89579ec666353', '5a6e9eecf16ae13a05a9f0ac5f1bacaace1593ff', '1ed58e08eeeb1e7777f4c17f05a136bd7b7e4951', '4e0a8fc84e568867eff1cb7b76ca28330668ad34', '66fafa55a3aacf4604d31095cc39a274623b278f', 'b87d042f0fb2e669e0ae79731fd3913724b5542c', 'd905e5f3dab54983f0582099b1552ca93fd36552', 'b61751076bba263bbf93f9