                 endpoint=None, chunksize=None, human=True, api=None, multipart=False)`

2. 上传接口修改为, block_size 为默认分块大小, 现为 1M
`put(self, key, value, checksum=False, headers=None,
            handler=None, params=None, secret=None, block_size=(1024 *1024))`

3. 视频处理接口为
`pretreat(self, tasks, source, notify_url="""")`
 `tasks` 为视频处理参数, `source` 为以上传视频地址, `notify_url` 为回调通知地址

4. 视频处理进度查询接口为,
`status(self, taskids=None)`
`taskids` 为任务 `id` ",https://api.github.com/repos/upyun/python-sdk/issues/14,,2015-12-21T08:56:03Z,2015-12-21T08:56:03Z,20,1080,417,15,[],[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/upyun/python-sdk/pull/14.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/upyun/python-sdk/pulls/14/commits,010,"['c4a465d8d89ffd92aec7638e257ce66c78f367ac', '0d85ee029a45a9b74afd1da442dce01448b1862d', '67d035780b50d718695aebf16dd1ad2ead6ef18e', 'aacb4e20a73eb1f95e93e1cdcb3e2bb5d533b1a5', '0af8f3ac3d83649e02c4929640a1c9f7d1b82c2e', '6156f04acff4d142946681484dde31ed331ee688', 'ef3aea61a6a17c210dd8dd75107df3e260e8acc1', 'd9ddabdf78bb40b874232fcee61c5aaf7c4366ac', 'ac90ef28c94de837b7af9e442b6d156278ddd3aa', '80e55555fb3c46f6be73bde331ac831d8dd4893b', '01d8bec388462089f6b531637b99955825e9bbfb', 'f1431b5cc3f7fa39b29fe1fdf4de88cd41de287c', '84fd0932f4cffc096aa590abece706cb1d2d21c4', '051cd3eb43e52522d395882e1237a99198e65ece', 'e3facfd09ccff162ebced5dd0de283a8acde7092', 'ac65766a912a7b553be638ce44034164b61718ea', 'd44cba26b46277b8f083d0babb1f6b1893060815', '9f29c848d50e5a24c7811080f7953a556298fe1d', '72ea76e0edd84a9a25e23b8594c8e9123c3e832b', 'a417fc8ad2fad6ca72a98abf068312d69e4f8801']"
