10667,PullRequestEvent,2017-11-14 15:06:09+00:00,81612762,trailofbits/manticore,1017522,feliam,2314423.0,trailofbits,151493166,,New API for EVM analysis,closed,False,551,"A much more easy to use solidity biased API. 

* Contracts can be created directly from solidity sourcecode
`contract_account = seth.solidity_create_contract(source_code, owner=user_account)
`
* Better ABI support. Call specific contract function by name, python objects are serialized automatically
`#Potential overflow
contract_account.add(1, 100)
`
* Better reporting of function names and parameter
`TRANSACTION  3 - CALL
	 From: 0x1bfa530d5d685155e98cd7d9dd23f7b6a801cfef
	 To: 0x1bfa530d5d685155e98cd7d9dd23f7b6a801cfef
	 Value: 0 wei
	 Data: 1003e2d2000000000ffffffffffff88060900000e3b0bfffb8b004080000000000000000
	 Function:  add ( 0x000000000ffffffffffff88060900000e3b0bfffb8b004080000000000000000 )
`
* Link exceptions with solidity source_code
`REPORT: THROW  at:
     13    assert(sellerBalance >= value)
`
* Use symbolic values in transactions

.. and much much more..",https://api.github.com/repos/trailofbits/manticore/issues/551,2017-11-14T15:06:09Z,2017-11-14T15:06:09Z,2017-11-14T15:06:09Z,10,528,265,10,CONTRIBUTOR,[],[],[],feliam,1017522.0,User,False,[],https://github.com/trailofbits/manticore/pull/551.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/trailofbits/manticore/pulls/551/commits,010,"['7343f7152f31769462abe5f4cf544a4191928d20', 'ea1998b1c4f4e4190e2fd0b424123b7724c786c9', '1870139b24e0010c34e5ad4e786b009e5e7d4f0c', '21ff832ac883293fe782905efe9d773cca6b1136', '70df6d589580361814e3ec1a561c07ba1685ecae', 'cf9cbc23fa43801f1e695d68fe7cd432a0b13b6a', 'd2fdc262ba1134a0033ff9cd82f53a4dfd9c9c0d', '26d1cd84920732b4d6bac214b7ba6c4128592d60', 'b78a9fc980821e915e73ac1122337a9824ad234c', 'e938eb7ba724ca6175ecc697033d6d6eccd88f45']"
