10960,PullRequestEvent,2017-08-07 20:10:57+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,4346,lukesneeringer,2810941.0,GoogleCloudPlatform,91859128,,"Add a ""How to start a new service"" branch with sample commits and code",closed,False,2660,"@jonparrott and @waprin have both suggested something like this and my discussion with @mckoss today pushed me over the ""OK Jon and Bill"" edge.

