- The commit content and commit messages are actually important, so please review them
- Should this go in it's own branch (referred to from CONTRIBUTING.rst) or should we check it in to `master` (checking in to master will help keep it from going stale, but may make the commits harder to find)
- Is there an actual fake service we can talk to? @bjwatson do you know

