11787,PullRequestEvent,2017-08-17 17:44:00+00:00,17720373,crate/crash,38700,mfussenegger,4048232.0,crate,131867486,,Add support for tab indentation & backspace de-indentation,closed,False,212,"Adds support for indentation via tab. Only works in multi-line:

The following does nothing:

```
<tab>
```

This works:

```
create table t1 x (
<tab> -> 4 spaces
```

De-indentation:
```
create table t1 x(
    <bs> -> removes 4 spaces
```

In addition the auto-completion popup is only shown if at least 1 character has been typed.",https://api.github.com/repos/crate/crash/issues/212,2017-08-17T17:43:59Z,2017-08-17T17:43:59Z,2017-08-17T17:43:59Z,1,27,0,1,[],[],[],[],mfussenegger,38700.0,User,False,[],https://github.com/crate/crash/pull/212.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/crate/crash/pulls/212/commits,010,['33bee013801e716110ff5a4fb770c27f1f973350']
