12010,PullRequestEvent,2015-01-18 11:02:49+00:00,12407457,Exa-Networks/exabgp,1227755,thomas-mangin,5339170.0,Exa-Networks,27445502,,Allow generic attribute not only in single line but also multiple lines,closed,False,215,"eg.)
