12650,PullRequestEvent,2018-05-29 15:27:54+00:00,77478378,ethereum/py-evm,824194,pipermerriam,6250754.0,ethereum,190683941,,Return early in Kademlia.recv_ping if remote is this_node,closed,False,785,"### What was wrong?

Occasionally receiving a `ping` from `this_node`.

### How was it fixed?

Avoid trying to add `remote` to routing table if it is `this_node` and return early from `recv_ping` when `remote == this_node`.

