13050,PullRequestEvent,2017-10-27 03:48:31+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,318622,paulbouwer,6844498.0,Azure,148817170,,"Fix metadata, update base image version and add prompt.",closed,False,4767,"This PR updates the container image metadata to include the **version** value in the `org.label-schema.docker.cmd` label and also correctly render the `${HOME}` variable in that label.

**Existing:**
```powershell
PS> docker image inspect azuresdk/azure-cli-python:2.0.20 --format ""{{json .Config.Labels}}"" | ConvertFrom-Json | ConvertTo-Json
{
    ""org.label-schema.build-date"":  ""2017-10-19T18:26:52Z"",
    ""org.label-schema.description"":  ""The Azure CLI 2.0 is the new Azure CLI and is applicable when you use the Resource Manager deployment model."",
    ""org.label-schema.docker.cmd"":  ""docker run -v :/root -it azuresdk/azure-cli-python:\u003cversion\u003e"",
    ""org.label-schema.license"":  ""MIT"",
    ""org.label-schema.name"":  ""Azure CLI 2.0"",
    ""org.label-schema.schema-version"":  ""1.0"",
    ""org.label-schema.url"":  ""https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/overview"",
    ""org.label-schema.usage"":  ""https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-az-cli2#docker"",
    ""org.label-schema.vcs-url"":  ""https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli.git"",
    ""org.label-schema.vendor"":  ""Microsoft"",
    ""org.label-schema.version"":  ""2.0.20""
}
```
**Updated:**
```powershell
PS> docker image inspect azuresdk/azure-cli-python:2.0.20-test --format ""{{json .Config.Labels}}"" | ConvertFrom-Json | ConvertTo-Json
{
    ""maintainer"":  ""Microsoft"",
    ""org.label-schema.build-date"":  ""2017-10-26T00:38:26Z"",
    ""org.label-schema.description"":  ""The Azure CLI 2.0 is the new Azure CLI and is applicable when you use the Resource Manager deployment model."",
    ""org.label-schema.docker.cmd"":  ""docker run -v ${HOME}/.azure:/root/.azure -it azuresdk/azure-cli-python:2.0.20-test"",
    ""org.label-schema.license"":  ""MIT"",
    ""org.label-schema.name"":  ""Azure CLI 2.0"",
    ""org.label-schema.schema-version"":  ""1.0"",
    ""org.label-schema.url"":  ""https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/overview"",
    ""org.label-schema.usage"":  ""https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-az-cli2#docker"",
    ""org.label-schema.vcs-url"":  ""https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli.git"",
    ""org.label-schema.vendor"":  ""Microsoft"",
    ""org.label-schema.version"":  ""2.0.20-test""
}
```

This PR also changes the prompt in the container to `azure-cli`.

```powershell
PS> docker run -v ${HOME}/.azure:/root/.azure -it --rm azuresdk/azure-cli-python:2.0.20-test
azure-cli# az vm
--help                  convert                 encryption              list                    nic                     run-command             user
-h                      create                  extension               list-ip-addresses       open-port               show                    wait
assign-identity         deallocate              format-secret           list-sizes              perform-maintenance     start
availability-set        delete                  generalize              list-skus               redeploy                stop
boot-diagnostics        diagnostics             get-instance-view       list-usage              resize                  unmanaged-disk
capture                 disk                    image                   list-vm-resize-options  restart                 update
azure-cli# az vm
```

This PR also updates the container base image version to `python:3.6.3-alpine`.",https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/issues/4767,,2017-10-27T03:48:30Z,2017-10-27T03:48:30Z,7,4,3,1,MEMBER,[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli/pull/4767.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/pulls/4767/commits,010,"['e16b44cd02cecd4ea862adf9eaf7f5b2ba3de3f8', '033ae3b1a558e70f530cc799cd63a15878cd81b7', 'af4feb616e405c90d336cd7601fc1d482c2f8c88', '8b8d051a47c4a02ee0f4ba1bea20ba5ed54b2773', 'd48def0640ead4049b69860d0f6e802cc909036d', 'f58662ba9fe69561dd71ce7a3a8fe03bf72270bd', '68d4177107563daf4d5e813ddc8a0cf0a13368fb']"
