13927,PullRequestEvent,2018-02-19 18:08:21+00:00,102028727,remix/partridge,331023,invisiblefunnel,8146335.0,remix,170025026,,[RFC] Multi-file filtering,open,False,25,"I've tried a bunch of approaches to multi-file filtering and this seemed to be the best option because it:

- preserves all dependent rows (stops, stop times, etc.) of filtered trips
- abstracts away changes to the config graph
- doesn't add complexity to the feed class

```python
import partridge as ptg

_date, service_ids = ptg.read_busiest_date('gtfs.zip')

filters = {
    'trips.txt': {
        'service_id': service_ids,
    },
    'stop_times.txt': {
        'stop_id': '2541151',
        'stop_sequence': 5,
    },
}

feed = ptg.get_filtered_feed('TfNSW-2017-11-02.zip', filters)
```
",https://api.github.com/repos/remix/partridge/issues/25,,,2018-02-19T18:08:21Z,6,110,73,7,OWNER,[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/remix/partridge/pull/25.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/remix/partridge/pulls/25/commits,010,"['a2265eb5849484b9188cc84188ab2700504c741d', '75b15e9b2061ef7361bdefd5c3c54851a94bacc7', '5429988491572ae93ae1726568cabac87b3d0da4', 'fb2a0b624c412fdeabb06fe3b8e5ba918f7c11b1', '22d52a2d7f0eca400b5051f4a93920b0e01e05ff', '640d2a31ae715fe279ca87b220fc0a8b532bace1']"
