14565,PullRequestEvent,2018-03-23 14:14:39+00:00,75772625,secure-systems-lab/securesystemslib,3520883,vladimir-v-diaz,9352491.0,secure-systems-lab,177080813,,Edit .pyup.yml to change schedule from daily to weekly,closed,False,140,"**Fixes issue #**:

