<details>
  <summary>Changelog</summary>
  
  
   ### 3.3.0
   ```
   ------------------

Features
^^^^^^^^

* Added new fixtures ``django_mail_dnsname`` and ``django_mail_patch_dns``,
  used by ``mailoutbox`` to monkeypatch the ``DNS_NAME`` used in
  :py:mod:`django.core.mail` to improve performance and
  reproducibility.

