16061,PullRequestEvent,2017-10-29 18:27:04+00:00,28765925,home-assistant/netdisco,1444314,balloob,13844975.0,home-assistant,136614113,,Ignore non-utf8 ssdp responses in scan(),closed,False,140,"A Samsung printer on my LAN appears to return both utf-8 and non utf-8 responses to SSDP queries. The non utf-8 causes ssdp.py scan() method to fail. By ignoring UnicodeDecodeError exceptions, the scan continues and even the printer is discovered because it also sends an utf-8 response.",https://api.github.com/repos/home-assistant/netdisco/issues/140,2017-10-29T18:27:04Z,2017-10-29T18:27:04Z,2017-10-29T18:27:04Z,3,7,2,1,NONE,[],[],[],balloob,1444314.0,User,False,[],https://github.com/home-assistant/netdisco/pull/140.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/home-assistant/netdisco/pulls/140/commits,010,"['ab1e2264f8c13c19179db64115b6a70079640811', 'd3acf759bd15cb9292964202acc7b169384437f1', '7560741c27b5c742fa79c9ff3c316a9c3687884c']"
