1. sparkmagic: kernels for spark through livy client 
2. autovizwidget: ipywidget that inspects a pandas df and does visualization with plotly
3. hdijupyterutils: common code shared by the first two packages

Apart from putting everything into different folders, tackled this:
- Make the three packages ready to submit to PyPI
- Separate configs for sparkmagic and autovizwidget
