16176,PullRequestEvent,2018-01-08 13:52:44+00:00,46374199,IntelRealSense/librealsense,22654243,zivsha,14095512.0,IntelRealSense,161515373,,Record UX Improvements,closed,False,977,"Made several change to improve recording abilities in the SDK.

- Made recording a ""parasite"" of the real device, by hooking to whatever is needed to be recorded.
This allows 3 major changes (with reverse order of importance):
    1. The record sensors can now simply delegate calls to the real sensor (without adding logic)
    2. After creating a record device, users can now work with either the record device (and sensors) or the 
real device and sensors. All actions will still be recorded.
    3. Recording can be started during streaming
- Refactored device model view to support changes
- Added `textual_icon` type for a more expressive code
- Made recording a 1-click operation which saves files automatically to user's Documents folder
- Fixed bug of ""UNKNOWN"" string in SR300 visual preset combo box
- Added `get_file_name` to record device
- Touch ups to playback device in viewer
