16924,PullRequestEvent,2018-06-11 06:07:42+00:00,94455745,dask/dask-ml,3019665,jakirkham,17131925.0,dask,193862205,MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MTkzODYyMjA1,Call map_blocks with dtype in ParallelPostFit.fit,closed,False,209,"Follow-up to comment ( https://github.com/dask/dask-ml/issues/197#issuecomment-396105384 )

