17403,PullRequestEvent,2016-12-09 12:11:42+00:00,1360247,django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic,2115303,mjnaderi,19997027.0,django-polymorphic,97298996,,Add a failing test to demonstrate a bug,open,False,254,"We found a bug in our project, and after investigating, we found that where it comes from. So I created a failing test based on our issue.

In this test, removing `prefetch_related` from this line:

```python
my_teams = Team.objects.filter(user_profiles=user_c).prefetch_related('user_profiles').distinct()
```

or removing this ""for"" loop:

```python
for _ in my_teams:
    pass
```

resolves the issue, and test passes. But with both of them, test fails.",https://api.github.com/repos/django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic/issues/254,,,2016-12-09T12:11:42Z,1,54,0,1,[],[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic/pull/254.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic/pulls/254/commits,010,['0a43501434292955ba24901a08fda1f035060a26']
