17731,PullRequestEvent,2018-04-23 04:07:36+00:00,71932349,ray-project/ray,10732128,devin-petersohn,22125274.0,ray-project,183321133,,[DataFrame] Implement Inter-DataFrame operations,open,False,1937,"Implements the inter-DataFrame and scalar operations:

- `add`, `__add__`
- `radd`, `__radd__`
- `__iadd__`
- `sub`, `__sub__`, `subtract`
- `rsub`, `__rsub__`
- `__isub__`
- `mul`, `__mul__`, `multiply`
- `rmul`, `__rmul__`
- `div`, `__div__`, `divide`
- `floordiv`, `__floordiv__`
- `rfloordiv`, `__rfloordiv`
- `__ifloordiv__`
- `truediv`, `__truediv__`
- `rtruediv`, `__rtruediv__`
- `__itruediv__`
- `mod`, `__mod__`
- `rmod`, `__rmod__`
- `__imod__`
- `pow`, `__pow__`
- `rpow`, `__rpow`
- `__ipow__`

Depends on #1932, don't merge until after that is merged.",https://api.github.com/repos/ray-project/ray/issues/1937,,,2018-04-23T04:07:35Z,7,731,247,5,CONTRIBUTOR,[],[],[],,,,,[],https://github.com/ray-project/ray/pull/1937.patch,https://api.github.com/repos/ray-project/ray/pulls/1937/commits,010,"['c1eb8b5dc16dbdf363888e22977dd2d44714378f', '3e0a509e255cb1323d5a92862ca91870907150fa', 'ea76921713493c9d1639e1ccf858b3bd0a0370a5', '49f602f536ac965fa3ab4d465db4d2c9920f5226', '92a7c96dc4cf3e30bc23a4b90123a001f40e7494', '71ab6ad7237f727f2eb817d996d9eeb46239df4c', '811cf2ebd4eb443231b7717270392565c1aeafdf', '79a485aa560107adb06d246047b1b48570627065', '2e2a5b0125343432040472b8440b1be03eee8c1d', '9409d5859b9c2f1c8a684fc27ab5b826091f2c61', 'a21a548dafb12343a63e699d10af142162d56379', 'ac8aace718da581820d1e2afd146db6127fb5611', 'fd39b523053f92b29b9041245a030f5162e6d9ee', '2798d2f91c55c41b6b1629a6e801c94d81d81d71', 'b28b1c1e092d9cfff6208e32d70018774b93b5ce', '9e17cba8d1c9ab872886accaac9069f37fa0bb4c', 'a25c90dc08bd9fd7962c22ff2b4ba4410fe4fec1', '5a436c8851a115e1642ba04ae23ffb42ab2d6687', 'd946fb549b6967fa80402539ec17e4ae315ed25b', 'f705a8fe5ba69be76ebeab4c93b067225a06f588', '736eb435db53309860310059524d2ae4b79abb59', '776e36d767e8f444820dfdeac3cdea5c5fe581ed']"
