18277,PullRequestEvent,2018-01-24 07:04:54+00:00,102692863,onnx/onnx,30275821,houseroad,31675368.0,onnx,161458327,,Introduce ONNX IR and Optimizer,closed,False,400,"Summary of the PR:
1) IR structures: onnx/ir.h
2) IR <--> protobuf converter: onnx/ir_pb_converter.cpp
3) optimizer: onnx/optimize.cpp

The optimizer supports:
1) fuse consecutive transposes,
2) fuse transpose(s) into GEMM op,
3) eliminate non-op transposes,
